Package net.sf.marineapi.provider.event

Contains event classes and listener interfaces for Providers.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
HeadingListener Listener interface for HeadingProvider.
ProviderListener<T extends ProviderEvent> Base interface for provider listeners.
TPVListener Listener interface for GPS time/position/velocity events.
 

Class Summary
HeadingEvent HeadingProvider event, reports the current magnetic/true heading of vessel in degrees.
ProviderEvent Abstract base class for provider events.
TPVEvent GPS time/position/velocity report with current position, altitude, speed, course and a time stamp.
